{
    for(int i=0;i&lt;5;i++)
    {
        System.out.print(&quot;Enter marks of subject &quot;+(i+1)+&quot;: &quot;);
        m[i] = sc.nextInt();
        avg += m[i];
    }

    avg /= 5;
}
```

And then, you can call each method, from _main_, as follows.

```java
